nitoring. </span></li></ul><p style="padding-top:0pt;color:#000000;padding-left:0;font-size:10pt;padding-bottom:0.5pt;line-height:1.1166666666666667;margin-right:0;margin-left:-0.2pt;text-indent:77.2pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;;margin-top:0;orphans:2;margin-bottom:0;widows:2;text-align:justify;padding-right:0"><span style="font-weight:700;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">Novitech (Virtual internship) - </span><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:10pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;font-style:normal">&nbsp;Chennai, TamilNadu &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Jan 2025 - Mar 2025 </span></p><ul class="lst-kix_list_1-0" style="padding:0;margin:0"><li style="padding-top:0pt;color:#000000;padding-left:0pt;font-size:10pt;padding-bottom:0.5pt;line-height:1.1166666666666667;margin-right:0;margin-left:36pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;;margin-top:0;orphans:2;margin-bottom:0;widows:2;text-align:justify;padding-right:0"><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:10pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;font-style:normal">Gained hands-on exposure to microcontroller programming, circuit simulation, and real time applications. </span></li><li style="padding-top:0pt;color:#000000;padding-left:0pt;font-size:10pt;padding-bottom:2.5pt;line-height:1.1166666666666667;margin-right:0;margin-left:36pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;;margin-top:0;orphans:2;margin-bottom:0;widows:2;text-align:justify;padding-right:0"><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:10pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;font-style:normal">Strengthened understanding of real-world applications of electronics through guided project tasks and mentorship. </span></li></ul><p style="padding-top:0pt;color:#000000;padding-left:0;font-size:10pt;padding-bottom:2.5pt;line-height:1.1166666666666667;margin-right:0;margin-left:36pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;;margin-top:0;orphans:2;margin-bottom:0;widows:2;height:10pt;text-align:justify;padding-right:0"><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:10pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;font-style:normal"></span></p><h1 style="padding-top:0pt;color:#000000;font-weight:700;padding-left:0;font-size:12pt;padding-bottom:1.1pt;line-height:1.0791666666666666;page-break-after:avoid;margin-right:0;margin-left:-0.2pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;;margin-top:0;orphans:2;margin-bottom:0;widows:2;text-align:justify;padding-right:0"><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:700;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:12pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;font-style:normal">PROJECTS </span></h1><p style="padding:0;margin:0;color:#000000;font-size:10pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;;line-height:1.1541666666666666;orphans:2;widows:2;text-align:justify"><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px 0.00px; border: 0.00px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 710.67px; height: 1.33px;"><img alt="" src="https://docs.google.com/drawings/d/1Ok_5TVgDMmHKioZl6XNKNCgjRjmUc39u45hpRYWE3nQDNnBxDzOxzH3qq_p-4CVDvr950S4-00-X8pf73FJ4_5Dq2XH6/image?parent=1N30wTEWjO2OZEOYkuobvr9o6nADi6rMb&amp;rev=1&amp;drawingRevisionAccessToken=miqE8u07tIFCIA&amp;h=1&amp;w=710&amp;ac=1" style="width: 710.67px; height: 1.33px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span></p><p style="padding:0;margin:0;color:#000000;font-size:10pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;;line-height:1.1541666666666666;orphans:2;widows:2;text-align:justify"><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:700;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:10pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;font-style:normal">Noise-Resistant Digital Transmission of Industrial Vibration Data | STM32, LDPC, CRC</span></p><ul class="lst-kix_list_5-0 start" style="padding:0;margin:0"><li style="padding:0;color:#000000;font-size:10pt;line-height:1.1541666666666666;margin-right:0;margin-left:36pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;;margin-top:0;orphans:2;margin-bottom:0;widows:2;text-align:justify"><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:10pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;font-style:normal">Developed a dual-microcontroller system (STM32 + ESP32) for real-time motor vibration data acquisition and wired transmission in industrial environments.</span></li><li style="padding:0;color:#000000;font-size:10pt;line-height:1.1541666666666666;margin-right:0;margin-left:36pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;;margin-top:0;orphans:2;margin-bottom:0;widows:2;text-align:justify"><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:10pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;font-style:normal">Implemented LDPC and CRC in Embedded C to achieve noise-resistant communication and improved Bit Error Rate (BER) performance.</span></li></ul><p style="padding:0;margin:0;color:#000000;font-size:10pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;;line-height:1.1541666666666666;orphans:2;widows:2;text-align:justify"><span style="font-weight:700;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">Smart &nbsp;Door Lock System</span><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:12pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;font-style:normal">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p><ul class="lst-kix_list_4-0 start" style="padding:0;margin:0"><li style="padding:0;color:#000000;font-size:10pt;line-height:1.1541666666666666;margin-right:0;margin-left:36pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;;margin-top:0;orphans:2;margin-bottom:0;widows:2;text-align:justify"><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:10pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;font-style:normal">Built a Bluetooth-based smart lock using ESP32 and servo motor with a custom MIT App Inventor mobile app.</span></li><li style="padding:0;color:#000000;font-size:10pt;line-height:1.1541666666666666;margin-right:0;margin-left:36pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;;margin-top:0;orphans:2;margin-bottom:0;widows:2;text-align:justify"><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:10pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;font-style:normal">Integrated &nbsp;a login based locking and unlocking with offline control . &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></li></ul><p style="padding-top:0pt;color:#000000;padding-left:0;font-size:10pt;padding-bottom:0.8pt;line-height:1.0791666666666666;margin-right:0;margin-left:-0.2pt;text-indent:77.2pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;;margin-top:0;orphans:2;margin-bottom:0;widows:2;text-align:justify;padding-right:0"><span style="font-weight:700;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">Smart Gas Detection &amp; Ventilation Control System </span></p><ul class="lst-kix_list_2-0 start" style="padding:0;margin:0"><li style="padding-top:0pt;color:#000000;padding-left:0pt;font-size:10pt;padding-bottom:0.5pt;line-height:1.1166666666666667;margin-right:0;margin-left:36pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;;margin-top:0;orphans:2;margin-bottom:0;widows:2;text-align:justify;padding-right:0"><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:10pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;font-style:normal">Developed a real-time lot-based air monitoring system using Raspberry Pi and multiple gas sensors (MQ135, I'M55003, MH-219) to detect harmful gases like NHŌéé, COŌéé, and dust (PM2.5) in fertilizer Industries. </span></li></ul><p style="padding-top:0pt;color:#000000;padding-left:0;font-size:10pt;padding-bottom:2.8pt;line-height:1.0791666666666666;margin-right:0;margin-left:18pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;;margin-top:0;orphans:2;margin-bottom:0;widows:2;text-align:justify;padding-right:0"><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:10pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;font-style:normal">ŌŚÅ &nbsp; &nbsp; Integrated ThingSpeak for cloud alerts and automated ventilation control using Python.</span></p><p style="padding-top:0pt;color:#000000;padding-left:0;font-size:10pt;padding-bottom:2.8pt;line-height:1.0791666666666666;margin-right:0;margin-left:18pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;;margin-top:0;orphans:2;margin-bottom:0;widows:2;height:10pt;text-align:justify;padding-right:0"><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:10pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;font-style:normal"></span></p><h1 style="padding-top:0pt;color:#000000;font-weight:700;padding-left:0;font-size:12pt;padding-bottom:1.1pt;line-height:1.0791666666666666;page-break-after:avoid;margin-right:0;margin-left:-0.2pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;;margin-top:0;orphans:2;margin-bottom:0;widows:2;text-align:justify;padding-right:0"><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:700;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:12pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;font-style:normal">CERTIFICATION </span></h1><p style="padding-top:0pt;margin:0;color:#000000;padding-left:0;font-size:10pt;padding-bottom:1.1pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;;line-height:1.0791666666666666;orphans:2;widows:2;text-align:justify;padding-right:0"><span style="overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px 0.00px; border: 0.00px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 710.67px; height: 1.33px;"><img alt="" src="https://docs.google.com/drawings/d/1qc2OSrCOTwwDDmRMlbw_ssDfbKZBfmA4axlKyrSlG1PjQlO4k7FHZQ3W9cyVHmrk2hEEMu1W8lm70-pIIAjqBqsjtRqb/image?parent=1N30wTEWjO2OZEOYkuobvr9o6nADi6rMb&amp;rev=1&amp;drawingRevisionAccessToken=zlwFwUMtQoBStA&amp;h=1&amp;w=710&amp;ac=1" style="width: 710.67px; height: 1.33px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);" title=""></span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-weight:700;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;</span></p><ul class="lst-kix_list_6-0 start" style="padding:0;margin:0"><li style="padding-top:0pt;color:#000000;padding-left:2.7pt;font-size:10pt;padding-bottom:1.1pt;line-height:1.0791666666666666;margin-right:0;margin-left:36pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;;margin-top:0;orphans:2;margin-bottom:0;widows:2;text-align:justify;padding-right:0"><span style="font-weight:400;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">Python</span><span style="font-weight:700;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;</span><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:10pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;font-style:normal">Programming, Generative AI , AIML - GUVI</span></li><li style="padding-top:0pt;color:#000000;padding-left:2.7pt;font-size:10pt;padding-bottom:1.1pt;line-height:1.0791666666666666;margin-right:0;margin-left:36pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;;margin-top:0;orphans:2;margin-bottom:0;widows:2;text-align:justify;padding-right:0"><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:10pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;font-style:normal">IC chip design and Verification - NM</span></li><li style="padding-top:0pt;color:#000000;padding-left:2.7pt;font-size:10pt;padding-bottom:1.1pt;line-height:1.0791666666666666;margin-right:0;margin-left:36pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;;margin-top:0;orphans:2;margin-bottom:0;widows:2;text-align:justify;padding-right:0"><span style="font-weight:400;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">Embedded systems and Raspberry</span><span style="font-weight:700;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;</span><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:10pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;font-style:normal">pi - NM</span></li><li style="padding-top:0pt;color:#000000;padding-left:2.7pt;font-size:10pt;padding-bottom:1.1pt;line-height:1.0791666666666666;margin-right:0;margin-left:36pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;;margin-top:0;orphans:2;margin-bottom:0;widows:2;text-align:justify;padding-right:0"><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:10pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;font-style:normal">Verilog VLSI - NSIC</span></li></ul></div></div></div></div></body></html>
